\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104myn1665702646849.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/myn1665702646849.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/myn1665702646849.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"myn1665702646849\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Determines whether labels (annotations) are displayed for each major tick. <code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">True</code> (default) or <code class=\"ph codeph\">False</code>.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"myn1665702646849__p_d108908e1_d108909e1_d108910e1\">Annotation<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">\"</code><code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">True</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">False</code>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">\"</code></p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"myn1665702646849__table_d12827e1_d12828e1_d12829e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"myn1665702646849__table_d12827e1_d12828e1_d12829e1__entry__1\">Value</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"myn1665702646849__table_d12827e1_d12828e1_d12829e1__entry__2\">Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"myn1665702646849__table_d12827e1_d12828e1_d12829e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">True</code>\n                     (default)</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"myn1665702646849__table_d12827e1_d12828e1_d12829e1__entry__2\">Annotation labels are displayed at each major\n                     tick.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"myn1665702646849__table_d12827e1_d12828e1_d12829e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">False</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"myn1665702646849__table_d12827e1_d12828e1_d12829e1__entry__2\">No annotations are displayed.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"myn1665702646849__section_tw4_hqb_bxb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1173777e120\">Example: Setting in ProcScript</h2>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"myn1665702646849__pre_mny_3qb_bxb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">$fieldproperties(METER) = \"annotation=false\"</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"myn1665702646849__section_dbm_jqb_bxb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1173777e129\">Applies To</h2>\n<p class=\"p\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"bwv1665702644903.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bwv1665702644903.html\" title=\"The umeter widget displays the value of a Numeric field on a gauge for which there is a predefined range of values marked around the outer edge. Uniface provides a logical widget called Meter, which is mapped to umeter.\">umeter (Meter)</a></p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3614713\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3614713\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Visible Annotation ( Annotation) Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 11, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Determines whether labels (annotations) are displayed for each major tick. True (default) or False . Annotation = \" True | False \" Value Description True (default) Annotation labels are displayed at each major tick. False No annotations are displayed. Example: Setting in ProcScript $fieldproperties(METER) = \"annotation=false\" Copy Applies To umeter (Meter) Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}